# Vue 3 Frontend Development Rules

## Vue Component Structure
- Use **Composition API** with `<script setup lang="ts">`
- Import components from [apps/admin-web/src/components/](mdc:apps/admin-web/src/components/)
- Follow the pattern in [App.vue](mdc:apps/admin-web/src/App.vue)

## State Management
- Use **Pinia** for global state: [apps/admin-web/src/stores/](mdc:apps/admin-web/src/stores/)
- Use **TanStack Query** for server state: [packages/api-client/src/](mdc:packages/api-client/src/)
- Query keys defined in [packages/api-client/src/queryKeys.ts](mdc:packages/api-client/src/queryKeys.ts)

## API Integration
- Use typed API client from [packages/api-client/src/](mdc:packages/api-client/src/)
- Import models from [packages/models/src/](mdc:packages/models/src/)
- Example: `import { invoicesApi } from '@neibrpay/api-client'`

## Styling
- Use **Tailwind CSS** for styling
- Configuration: [apps/admin-web/tailwind.config.js](mdc:apps/admin-web/tailwind.config.js)
- Global styles: [apps/admin-web/src/style.css](mdc:apps/admin-web/src/style.css)

## Routing
- Vue Router configuration: [apps/admin-web/src/router/](mdc:apps/admin-web/src/router/)
- Use route-based code splitting

## TypeScript
- Strict TypeScript enabled in [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)
- Use proper typing for all props, emits, and composables
- Import types from [packages/models/src/](mdc:packages/models/src/)

## File Organization
- Components: `src/components/`
- Views: `src/views/`
- Composables: `src/composables/`
- Services: `src/services/`
- Config: `src/config/`